attributes.title: Patron
attributes.description:
• Supporting Our Content

You are contributing directly to making more of the projects you love.

From the bottom of my heart, THANK YOU!

  • Patreon-Only Exclusive Videos (30+ videos)

Access to a growing catalog of videos that will not get to YouTube. Topics range from tutorials, animation lessons, building an art career, the industry, to self-motivation.

  • Access to Manu's Animation VaultÂ (10+ sequences)

Clip Studio Files, After Effects Files (with all layers and frames), Final Renders, and Process Breakdowns on a selection of the best animations I've created (that I'm allowed to share).Â 

  • YouTube Insights Blog Access (15+ In-depth breakdowns)

Posts sharing everything I know on how YouTube works, its Algorithm, Idea Generation, Making successful videos, and any other Tips I can give you.

  • 'Patron' Role in our Discord Server

Get a distinct role and name color in our community.

  • A tight, but not uncomfortable nor awkward virtual hug!

attributes.title: Champion
attributes.description:
• Patreon Module for Foundry VTT: Gain access to our always updating Foundry Moudle for your own Foundry games!

  • Subclasses: Custom-made subclasses to introduce to your table to bring new life to your games.

  • Elite and Boss Creatures: Stat Blocks that feature our Elite and Boss CR systems and Phase Combat allow you to bring Boss Fights to your 5e games.

  • Homebrew Systems: New systems crafted by Io Publishing, available to you before book releases for testing at your table! Your input will flesh out our systems, allowing them to be the best they can be.

  • And more...! This is where our most custom content goes as we work on it!

  • ... and previous tier rewards!

  • Join the IO Discord (be sure to link your Patreon Account to your Discord Account) : http://www.discord.gg/worldofio

The Emperor, immortal through the faith of his people, had influenced the most powerful of Radiant and Voidtouch to take up arms against those who may defy his will. Inevitably, his citizens rose against his wicked rule, and we stood with them. The Emperor sent out his Dread Knights to begin his violent culling - earning him the title "Dread Emperor." His dark legacy would end with my mother's blade.
